'''慢性阻塞性肺病'''（{{lang-en|Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease}}，[[缩写|缩写]]为'''{{lang|en|COPD}}'''），常简称为'''肺阻塞'''。是一种以持续性的气流受限为特征的{{link-en|阻塞性肺疾病|Obstructive lung disease}}<ref name="GOLD2017Chp1">{{cite book|url=http://goldcopd.org/download/326/|title=Global Strategy for the Diagnosis, Management and Prevention of COPD|last=Algusti|first=Alvar G. et al.|publisher=Global Initiative for Chronic Obstructive Lung Disease (GOLD)|year=2017|pages=6–17|chapter=Definition and Overview|access-date=2018-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170830200015/http://goldcopd.org/download/326/|archive-date=2017-08-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref><!--p. 6--><ref name="Roversi2017">{{cite journal|title=GOLD 2017 recommendations for COPD patients: toward a more personalized approach|first1=Sara|last2=Corbetta|first2=Lorenzo|date=5 May 2017|journal=COPD Research and Practice|doi=10.1186/s40749-017-0024-y|volume=3|last3=Clini|first3=Enrico|last1=Roversi}}</ref>。其主要症状[[气短|呼吸短促]]、[[咳嗽|咳嗽]]和{{link-en|咳痰|Sputum}}<ref name="GOLD2017Chp1" /><!--pp. 25–26-->，常被誤認為感冒或氣喘，因此超過八成確診時已經是中重度。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Respiratory Pharmacotherapy Use in Patients Newly Diagnosed with Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease in a Primary Care Setting in the UK: A Retrospective Cohort Study|url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.3109/15412555.2014.922064|last=Wurst|first=Keele E.|last2=Shukla|first2=Amit|date=2014-09|journal=COPD: Journal of Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease|issue=5|doi=10.3109/15412555.2014.922064|volume=11|pages=521–530|language=en|issn=1541-2555|last3=Muellerova|first3=Hana|last4=Davis|first4=Kourtney J.|access-date=2020-04-08|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805020138/https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.3109/15412555.2014.922064|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Characteristics of Patients with Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease at the First Visit to a Pulmonary Medical Center in Korea: The KOrea COpd Subgroup Study Team Cohort|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.3346/jkms.2016.31.4.553|last=Lee|first=Jung Yeon|last2=Chon|first2=Gyu Rak|date=2016|journal=Journal of Korean Medical Science|issue=4|doi=10.3346/jkms.2016.31.4.553|volume=31|pages=553|issn=1011-8934|last3=Rhee|first3=Chin Kook|last4=Kim|first4=Deog Kyeom|last5=Yoon|first5=Hyoung Kyu|last6=Lee|first6=Jin Hwa|last7=Yoo|first7=Kwang Ha|last8=Lee|first8=Sang Haak|last9=Lee|first9=Sang Yeub}}</ref>COPD是一種{{Le|進行性疾病|progressive disease}}，病情會隨時間逐漸惡化<ref name="GOLD2013Chp1">{{cite book|url=http://www.atsjournals.org/doi/full/10.1164/rccm.201204-0596PP#.V5Fh3_mANBc|title=Global Strategy for the Diagnosis, Management, and Prevention of Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease|last=Vestbo|first=Jørgen|publisher=Global Initiative for Chronic Obstructive Lung Disease|year=2013|pages=1–7|chapter=Definition and Overview|access-date=2018-05-25|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308040107/https://www.atsjournals.org/doi/full/10.1164/rccm.201204-0596PP#.V5Fh3_mANBc|dead-url=no}}</ref>，最後連走路、著衣等日常活動都難以進行<ref name="WHO2015">{{cite web|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs315/en/|title=Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD) Fact sheet N°315|accessdate=4 March 2016|date=January 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304082716/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs315/en/|archivedate=4 March 2016|website=WHO|deadurl=no|df=}}</ref>。疾病具不可逆性，研究顯示肺阻塞病人急性發作住院的死亡率為4%，年齡越大及共病症越多的病人，住院死亡率也越高，而病人出院後一年的死亡率高達22%。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=In-Hospital and One-Year Mortality and Their Predictors in Patients Hospitalized for First-Ever Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease Exacerbations: A Nationwide Population-Based Study|url=http://dx.plos.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0114866|last=Ho|first=Te-Wei|last2=Tsai|first2=Yi-Ju|date=2014-12-09|journal=PLoS ONE|issue=12|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0114866|editor-last=Bai|editor-first=Chunxue|volume=9|pages=e114866|language=en|issn=1932-6203|pmc=PMC4260959|pmid=25490399|last3=Ruan|first3=Sheng-Yuan|last4=Huang|first4=Chun-Ta|last5=Lai|first5=Feipei|last6=Yu|first6=Chong-Jen|last7=The HINT Study Group}}</ref> 過去學界會將COPD分為'''慢性支氣管炎'''（Chronic bronchitis）和'''肺氣腫'''（emphysema）兩型<ref name="WHO2015" /><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=li1VCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA913|title=Ferri's netter patient advisor|first1=John A.|date=2012|publisher=Saunders|isbn=9781455728268|edition=2nd|page=913|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908185428/https://books.google.com/books?id=li1VCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA913|archivedate=2017-09-08|deadurl=no|last1=Craig|df=}}</ref>。[[慢性支氣管炎|慢性支氣管炎]]一詞現今則用於描述除外慢性咳嗽的其他已知原因后，病人每年咳嗽、咳痰三个月以上并连续两年者；而[[肺气肿|肺气肿]]是指肺部终末细支气管远端气腔出现异常持久的扩张，并伴有肺泡和细支气管的破坏，而无明显的肺纤维化。<ref>{{cite book |title=内科学 |publisher=人民卫生出版社 |isbn=9787117265416 |page=21 |edition=9th}}</ref>

[[吸烟|吸烟]]是导致慢性阻塞性肺病的最主要的原因。其他相对次要的因素包括[[空气污染|空气污染]]和[[遗传|遗传]]等<ref name="Lancet2012">{{cite journal|title=Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease|date=April 2012|journal=Lancet|issue=9823|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(11)60968-9|volume=379|pages=1341–51|pmid=22314182|vauthors=Decramer M, Janssens W, Miravitlles M}}</ref>。在[[发展中国家|发展中国家]]，导致空气污染最常见的原因是[[烹调|烹煮]]及[[供暖|供暖]]炉火的通風不良<ref name="WHO2015" />。长期暴露在这样的環境下，会使肺部产生[[炎症|炎症反应]]，并导致小气道变窄及肺组织的破坏<ref name="GOLD2007">{{cite journal|title=Global strategy for the diagnosis, management, and prevention of chronic obstructive pulmonary disease: GOLD executive summary|url=http://ajrccm.atsjournals.org/content/176/6/532.long|date=September 2007|journal=Am. J. Respir. Crit. Care Med.|issue=6|doi=10.1164/rccm.200703-456SO|volume=176|pages=532–55|pmid=17507545|vauthors=Rabe KF, Hurd S, Anzueto A, Barnes PJ, Buist SA, Calverley P, Fukuchi Y, Jenkins C, Rodriguez-Roisin R, van Weel C, Zielinski J|access-date=2015-03-27|archive-date=2013-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130102150149/http://ajrccm.atsjournals.org/content/176/6/532.long|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。这一诊断是以{{link-en|肺功能测试|Pulmonary function tsting}}所给出的气流受限为基础<ref name="Nathell">{{cite journal|title=COPD diagnosis related to different guidelines and spirometry techniques|journal=Respir. Res.|issue=1|doi=10.1186/1465-9921-8-89|year=2007|volume=8|page=89|pmc=2217523|pmid=18053200|vauthors=Nathell L, Nathell M, Malmberg P, Larsson K}}</ref>。COPD與[[哮喘|哮喘]]不同的是，前者在使用[[支气管扩张药|支气管扩张药]]之後，改善效果不若後者<ref name="WHO2015" />。

减少[[風險因子|風險因子]]的暴露可有效预防大多數慢性阻塞性肺病<ref name="Piro2012">{{cite journal|title=Smoking cessation and environmental hygiene|date=July 2012|journal=Med. Clin. North Am.|issue=4|doi=10.1016/j.mcna.2012.04.014|volume=96|pages=849–67|pmid=22793948|vauthors=Pirozzi C, Scholand MB}}</ref>。这包括尽可能地减少吸烟频率和改善室内外的空气质量<ref name="WHO2015" />。尽管治疗可以减缓病情恶化，但尚无治愈方法。<ref name="WHO2015" />慢性阻塞性肺病的治疗方式包括[[戒烟|戒烟]]、接种[[疫苗|疫苗]]、{{link-en|肺康复治疗|Pulmonary rehabilitation}}，以及常用的各种吸入性[[支气管扩张药|支气管扩张药]]和[[皮質類固醇|皮質類固醇]]<ref name="Lancet2012" />。有些患者还需要长期吸氧或[[肺移植|肺移植]]<ref name="GOLD2007" />。在遇到急性发作的患者时，可采取增加短效支氣管擴張药之劑量、用藥頻率以及[[住院|住院]]治疗的方式<ref name="Lancet2012" />。

2020年全球COPD的患者約有5.5億人（約7.4%)<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The global impact of Aspergillus infection on COPD|url=https://doi.org/10.1186/s12890-020-01259-8|last=Hammond|first=Emily E.|last2=McDonald|first2=Charles S.|date=2020-09-11|journal=BMC Pulmonary Medicine|issue=1|doi=10.1186/s12890-020-01259-8|volume=20|pages=241|issn=1471-2466|pmc=PMC7488557|pmid=32912168|last3=Vestbo|first3=Jørgen|last4=Denning|first4=David W.}}</ref>，其中大洋洲的罹患COPD的患者占比最高（約10.9%），非洲最低（約5.4%）。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The global impact of Aspergillus infection on COPD|author=|url=https://doi.org/10.1186/s12890-020-01259-8|last=Hammond|first=Emily E.|last2=McDonald|first2=Charles S.|date=2020-09-11|journal=BMC Pulmonary Medicine|issue=1|doi=10.1186/s12890-020-01259-8|volume=20|pages=241|issn=1471-2466|pmc=PMC7488557|pmid=32912168|last3=Vestbo|first3=Jørgen|last4=Denning|first4=David W.}}</ref>主要影響40歲以上的人口<ref name="WHO2015" />，男女罹病風險相當<ref name="WHO2015" />。1990年，COPD共約造成240萬人死亡；直到2019年，全球死亡人數上升至323萬人。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The top 10 causes of death|url=https://www.who.int/news-room/fact-sheets/detail/the-top-10-causes-of-death|access-date=2021-10-28|work=www.who.int|language=en|archive-date=2021-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210924191646/https://www.who.int/news-room/fact-sheets/detail/the-top-10-causes-of-death}}</ref>約80%的死亡人數分布於中低收入國家<ref name="WHO2015" />，可能肇因於較高的吸菸率<ref>{{cite journal|title=Projections of Global Mortality and Burden of Disease from 2002 to 2030|url=http://dx.plos.org/10.1371/journal.pmed.0030442|date=November 2006|journal=PLoS Med.|issue=11|doi=10.1371/journal.pmed.0030442|volume=3|pages=e442|pmc=1664601|pmid=17132052|vauthors=Mathers CD, Loncar D}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。另也可能因中低收入國家COPD治療指引覆蓋率（69.8%）較低（高收入國家覆蓋率為98.1%），民眾及醫療人員較難企及相關資料所致<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Gaps in COPD Guidelines of Low- and Middle-Income Countries: A Systematic Scoping Review|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/33038390|last=Tabyshova|first=Aizhamal|last2=Hurst|first2=John R.|date=2021-02|journal=Chest|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.chest.2020.09.260|volume=159|pages=575–584|issn=1931-3543|pmc=7856534|pmid=33038390|last3=Soriano|first3=Joan B.|last4=Checkley|first4=William|last5=Wan-Chun Huang|first5=Erick|last6=Trofor|first6=Antigona C.|last7=Flores-Flores|first7=Oscar|last8=Alupo|first8=Patricia|last9=Gianella|first9=Gonzalo|access-date=2021-10-28|archive-date=2022-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220504042510/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/33038390/}}</ref>。

2010年，慢性阻塞性肺病导致了21亿美元的经济损失<ref name="Cost20132">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=cRZaAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA143|title=Global problems, local solutions : costs and benefits|last=Lomborg|first=Bjørn|publisher=Cambridge University Press|year=2013|isbn=978-1-107-03959-9|page=143|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160517163338/https://books.google.com/books?id=cRZaAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA143|archivedate=2016-05-17|deadurl=no|df=}}</ref>。2016年已占全球死因第三位，是最嚴重的慢性疾病之一，根據衛生福利部死因統計顯示，台灣COPD目前為十大死因排名第7位，每年約5千人因肺阻塞死亡，2017年更高達6,260人死於肺阻塞。


